sentences: Alexander Joshua Solowitz (born December 15, 1979) is an American actor, composer, singer, dancer, and producer.
Solowitz appeared in the film Gardens of the Night with John Malkovich.
He also played Brett in the 1999 film Never Been Kissed, Bobby "911" in the 2006 film Alpha Dog, and Sebastian in the 2012 dark comedy Small Apartments.
